&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About&amp;nbsp;Us&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Broadsign is a growing software company with a mission to make buying, selling, and delivering out-of-home media easier than ever. Our software is operated by some of the most successful out-of-home businesses and powers impactful, compelling campaigns seen across the world. Come join us as&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;a&amp;nbsp;Full-Stack&amp;nbsp;Software&amp;nbsp;Developer&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;in Montreal!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About&amp;nbsp;the&amp;nbsp;Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Full-Stack Software Developer, you will play a pivotal role in driving the evolution of our industry-leading out-of-home media platforms by bridging the gap between robust backend architectures and sleek, responsive user interfaces. This role is designed for a developer who thrives on clean code and innovation, values strong engineering practices, and wants to see their work impact millions of viewers globally.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What&amp;nbsp;to&amp;nbsp;expect&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The&amp;nbsp;R&amp;amp;D&amp;nbsp;department&amp;nbsp;is&amp;nbsp;at&amp;nbsp;the&amp;nbsp;center&amp;nbsp;of&amp;nbsp;the&amp;nbsp;action&amp;nbsp;at&amp;nbsp;Broadsign.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Your main focus will be to design and develop new features on both the front and back ends of our software suite. And because you’re a technology enthusiast, you’ll probably want to tweak and maintain our existing feature set as well! You’ll get to participate in sprints where you’ll be encouraged to share your ideas and knowledge with your team. You’ll be working in a dynamic and peer-driven environment where you’ll play with all the latest and greatest hardware and software!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What&amp;nbsp;you&amp;nbsp;need&amp;nbsp;to&amp;nbsp;perform&amp;nbsp;in&amp;nbsp;this&amp;nbsp;job&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3-7&amp;nbsp;years&amp;nbsp;of&amp;nbsp;experience&amp;nbsp;in&amp;nbsp;software&amp;nbsp;development&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Experience&amp;nbsp;working&amp;nbsp;with&amp;nbsp;object-oriented&amp;nbsp;languages&amp;nbsp;like&amp;nbsp;C#&amp;nbsp;(.NET&amp;nbsp;Core)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You&amp;nbsp;understand&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;use&amp;nbsp;the&amp;nbsp;SOLID&amp;nbsp;principles!&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You&amp;nbsp;have&amp;nbsp;used&amp;nbsp;tools&amp;nbsp;such&amp;nbsp;as&amp;nbsp;AWS&amp;nbsp;(CloudFormation,&amp;nbsp;ECS)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A&amp;nbsp;good&amp;nbsp;understanding&amp;nbsp;of&amp;nbsp;REST&amp;nbsp;APIs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience&amp;nbsp;writing&amp;nbsp;testable&amp;nbsp;code&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;be&amp;nbsp;familiar&amp;nbsp;with&amp;nbsp;TDD&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong&amp;nbsp;belief&amp;nbsp;in&amp;nbsp;agile&amp;nbsp;principles&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience&amp;nbsp;with&amp;nbsp;SQL&lt;/li&gt;
